    <item>
      <title>以色列誓言对伊朗袭击进行报复，油价继续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向以色列发射约 200 枚弹道导弹，导致以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡誓言进行报复，并加大了该地区原油供应的风险，油价连续第二天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 22:51:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国期货因紧张等待以色列回应而下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东局势紧张，市场进入观望状态，美国期货下跌，美国国债回吐前一日的部分涨幅。油价上涨，黄金价格徘徊在历史高位附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 22:39:40 GMT</pubDate>
